{"tid":1356294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先識唔驚出街？","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T22:04:05.000Z","uid":266601,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4fbe3738b43c95b731a8ff7fe662d791c8d30116","tid":1356294,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"小弟大埔人，每次遊行，光復行動都有出。<br />\n<br />\n721上環，元朗，荃灣嘅事大家都知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n既然大家都想贏呢場抗爭，就要學識如何抗懼，唔再善忘。<br />\n<br />\n而家局勢好明顯，我地其實乜野都冇影響到啲野？<br />\n<br />\n-新城巿有冇因為我地去坐而企出黎作出回應？冇。<br />\n-元朗拉閘唔做生意係唔係我地影響？未必係。<br />\n-一啲吃吃喝喝不停去玩嘅港豬會唔會因為我地而覺醒？唔會囉，佢地係驚黑警，驚元朗牛屎佬周圍去先開始有心機去留意。<br />\n<br />\n點樣去做到贏呢場抗爭嘅兩點因素？<br />\n<br />\n-727企出黎，去元朗，唔入圍村，唔好怕俾人打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 企出黎話俾班鄉黑知道，我地並唔撚怕。<br />\n2. 既然我地都已經知道警黑勾結甚或有證據，佢地一郁我地，文宣手足識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 反抗，但非撩起人個皮，而係自衛。<br />\n<br />\n-文宣繼續宣傳721所有事件俾男女老少知道，又溫故知新，以達至不讓港人因善忘而忘卻左我地一路做嘅野<br />\n<br />\n見到文宣好努力，每天不停去做好自己工作，但文宣手足<span style=\"font-size: large;\">切勿忘記</span>5+1大訴求！俾人地知道翻我地一路以來係做緊啲乜，而目標又係啲乜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teBQQyB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteBQQyB.png&h=cc3a9f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KOS3Uj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KOS3Uj.png&h=999c4bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nANYWAY, See you in 7.27<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7e39c24638883f599978943c7ac1c20c369418","tid":1356294,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"希望阻你兩分鐘 簽一簽呢個petition <br />\n請求國際人道援助 保障市民人身安全同治安<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4SZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=62b77c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n7.27 元朗<br />\n______________________<br />\n我要真普選 <br />\n監控燈柱 社會評級制<br />\n幾條人命 黑警橫行無忌"},{"pid":"f6833db0bd98887cbd33b25bb970d1e744cb5d7b","tid":1356294,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"推 直到更有用嘅post出現之前，唔希望沉。"},{"pid":"ebe63629b057844726c3b6215ff7e9a20fef1b7e","tid":1356294,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"635c667f4821a5cdd2d3231b5d0ede2b03e22f32","tid":1356294,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a5cb1eab0255a376417fecded7242cbaea76e8f","tid":1356294,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"元朗早啲出發唔該"},{"pid":"c0d8b97d8508a5ea3b89aa723a12a66d3cac8593","tid":1356294,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"66b9518f8ea2913964dd819428964f5fdd2a5e22","tid":1356294,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"3152e8254083e667b4cba2412dc59c57ca7960c8","tid":1356294,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4SZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=7b60c2ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"a9e4cc36f41931cb8546d81c893a621afbf89b48","tid":1356294,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:57:59.00